PORT "API port"
DB_PATH "location of your database"
API "url to this api"
SECRET "to sign the jwt"
IMDB_USER_AGENT "realistic browser User-Agent for IMDB GraphQL requests"
IMDB_TIMEOUT "ms for IMDB HTTP requests (e.g. 15000)"
IMDB_GRAPHQL_ENDPOINT "override the IMDB GraphQL endpoint (default https://api.graphql.imdb.com/)"
IMDB_TZ "timezone used to decide if an episode already aired (default: system tz, e.g. America/Mexico_City)"
RSS_USER_AGENT "User-Agent for RSS/Atom feed fetches (e.g. MangaCafeRSS/1.0)"
RSS_TIMEOUT "ms for RSS HTTP requests (e.g. 15000)"
COMIVEX_USER_AGENT "User-Agent for scraping comivex.com (realistic browser UA)"
COMIVEX_TIMEOUT "ms for comivex HTTP requests (e.g. 15000)"
CUSTOM_SOURCE_USER_AGENT "User-Agent for fetching HTML in the generic source-config scraper (realistic browser UA)"
CUSTOM_SOURCE_TIMEOUT "ms for custom source HTTP requests (e.g. 15000)"
BUILD_OUT_DIR "where vite writes the frontend build (e.g. dist for dev, /srv/www/mangacafe.vip for prod served by nginx)"
MCAPTCHA_SITE_KEY "your mCAPTCHA site key"
MCAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY "Get this from mCAPTCHA settings site"
